song.title: Heaven 7 - Learning To Fly (Malmen's Soft Pedal Remix)
song.info: Hi everyone! I made this song in one day, rather like.. 5 hours. Speedcomposing at its finest. Also the song was made one day before the final deadline but I hope it will be okay for your ears, hehe.
